She turned her optics to Quet. "Scourge is not commander of the Ark. However, 
Rodimus Prime would have presedence over it above all of us."

She then turned to Kup. "Perhaps we should arrange a summit meeting with 
Rodimus upon this issue." The idea was something she was open to. Highly unusual 
for her. Her loathing for Autobots usually kept her from even associating with 
them.
